Retrieve variants from a musica or musica_result object

Source: R/methods.R
variants.Rd

The variants data.table contains the variants and variant-level annotations

variants(object)

# S4 method for musica
variants(object)

# S4 method for musica_result
variants(object)

variants(musica) <- value

# S4 method for musica,data.table
variants(musica) <- value

Arguments

object

A musica object generated by the create_musica function or a musica_result object generated by a mutational discovery or prediction tool.
musica

A musica object generated by the create_musica function
value

A data.table of mutational variants and variant-level annotations

Value

A data.table of variants

Examples
